name: electric motor production, for electric scooter | electric motor, for electric scooter | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/996/documentation

This dataset describes the production of an electric motor suitable for an electric scooter. The entries are given on a function of kg of device. The original data was collected for a device of approximately 5.8kg. The dataset is based on direct inspection of existing commercial devices of current technology.

The dataset takes as input the various marterials and energy resources required for the production of the electric motor.

The dataset returns the electric motor and production waste materials as by-products.
